<div id="source-australian-transport-assessment-and-planning-atap-guidelines-m1-public-transport-parameter-values-technical-report-douglas-2021-1" class="section level5 unlisted unnumbered hasAnchor">
<h5>Source: Australian Transport Assessment and Planning (ATAP) Guidelines – M1 Public Transport: Parameter Values Technical Report (Douglas, 2021)<a href="#source-australian-transport-assessment-and-planning-atap-guidelines-m1-public-transport-parameter-values-technical-report-douglas-2021-1" class="anchor-section" aria-label="Anchor link to header"></a></h5>
</div>
</div>
